com.estimote.sdk.eddystone

Class Eddystone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.sdk.eddystone.Eddystone
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    public class Eddystone
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Immutable representation of Eddystone-UID & Eddystone-URL beacons.

    Eddystone beacon can either transmit Eddystone-UID or Eddystone-URL packet. Never both.

    Periodically beacon sends telemetry information. Available in telemetry field along with time it was seen telemetryLastSeenMillis.
